BEGIN_TEXT
This problem corresponds to Problem 2.27 in the text. 
$PAR
a) The value of \( \displaystyle \int_0^{ \infty } \delta(t) [ $b2 e^{-$b1 t} + $b3 \sin(2 \pi 10^6 t ) ] dt \) is
$PAR

 \{ans_rule(20)\}
$PAR

